data.description: Come See This Near Brand New, Spacious, 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Home Located Near the Many Amenities Othello Has to Offer. This Home Features an Open Concept Kitchen/Living Room/Dining Area, Pantry, Kitchen Island, Large Living Room, Utility Room, and Den/Office on the Main Level. Great News.. All Appliances Stay! Second Floor has a Family Area with Master Suite.  This Home is Additionally Equipped with a Two Car Garage, Backyard Patio, and Underground Sprinklers.
